title: ASML Weekly News Summary
body: Over the past week, ASML has not released any new press releases or significant news updates. The most recent information available pertains to their third-quarter 2025 financial results, published in October 2025. In that quarter, ASML reported net sales of €7.5 billion and a net income of €2.1 billion. The company also provided guidance for the fourth quarter, expecting net sales between €9.2 billion and €9.8 billion, with a gross margin between 51% and 53%. ([ourbrand.asml.com](https://ourbrand.asml.com/m/6426a12faab0f2a0/original/ASML-Press-Release-Quarterly-Results-Q3-2025.pdf?utm_source=openai))

key_points.text: No new press releases or significant news updates from ASML in the past week.
Most recent financial results from Q3 2025 show net sales of €7.5 billion and net income of €2.1 billion.
Q4 2025 guidance anticipates net sales between €9.2 billion and €9.8 billion, with a gross margin between 51% and 53%.
